data.description: 142 Chaste Tree Circle in Liberty Village is a must-see home. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this house offers plenty of space for those who love to entertain. The private back yard is perfect for outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying some peace and quiet.Inside, you'll find recent paint updates that give the home a fresh and modern feel. The screened-in back porch is a great spot to relax and enjoy the outdoors without worrying about bugs.One of the standout features of this home is the walk-in closets in every bedroom. No more fighting over closet space - everyone will have plenty of room for their belongings.The open floor plan allows for easy movement throughout the house, making it a breeze to entertain guests or keep an eye on whatever mischief is beinggotten into in the other room.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, with gas appliances and soft-close cabinets. Cooking and cleaning up will be a breeze in this well-appointed space.  The fenced-in back yard provides a safe and secure space to play.  Despite being only a few years old, this home has a timeless charm that will never go out of style.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 142 Chaste Tree Circle your home. Schedule a showing today and see all that this inviting house has to offer.
